title: El Encanto de la Naturaleza
description: A natural goods specialty shop, where you can find many seeds and vegetarian/vegan items like flaxseed, sesame seed, pumpkin seed, chia seed, amaranth, dried fruits and nuts, dates, figs. Will also special order tofu for you. Located one block from the Central Acapulco market. Owner does not speak English, but is very helpful.
